By God, dear brother, the number of the village, the houses
of Xezwê... there is a total of 400 houses. It has 400
houses.

147
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:35,000
Û xelkê wî jî teqrîben... hejmara xelkê gundê Xezwê... tu
karî bêjî 2500 û zêdetir jî heye jiyana xwe li gundê Xezwê
dikin.
 
And its people roughly... the number of people of Xezwê
village... you could say 2500 and more are living in Xezwê
village.

148
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:38,000
Hemî kurd in?
 
Are they all Kurds?

149
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:38,000
Belê, belê, hemî kurd in... Malek ereb têde heye. Malek ereb
