153
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,000
Belê.
 
Yes.

154
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:27,000
Ev malbat, çend malbat li gund hene?
 
These families, how many families are in the village?

155
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:47,000
Bixwedê birê delal... nêzîka tu karî bêjî dehs malbat di
