Îslêm family exists... the Mihkê family exists... the Kedê
family exists... the Hesenkê family exists... the Kêfo
family exists, this is also an ancient family of course...
maybe the second number when they came to settle in the
village was the Kêfo family anyway, it's a large family,
yes.

156
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:12,000
