184
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:48,000
Hemî piraniya wê darên hinarê ne.
 
Yes.

185
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:51,000
Hemî piraniya wê darên hinarê ne.
 
Most of them are pomegranate trees.

186
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:52,000
Belê.
 
Yes.

187
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:57,000
E, ez dixwazim tiştekî din ji te re bibêjim... Sibehê da
cejn e.
 
Uh, I want to tell you something else... Tomorrow is a
holiday.

188
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:58,000
Cejna Xidir Liyas e.
 
It's the Xidir Liyas holiday.

189
00:15:58,000 --> 00:15:59,000
Belê.
 
Yes.

190
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:11,000
E... destpêkê em ji we hemîya pîroz dikin... Cejna we...
Cejna we cejna teva bê.
 
Uh... firstly we congratulate all of you... Your holiday...
May your holiday be everyone's holiday.

191
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:31,000
Ser çava, ser çava. Em ji we re jî, û li kurdên me, li
hemîyan pîroz be... Ev Cejna Xidir Liyas... hecî Cejna
Mirazan e... cejna xêrê ye, cejna silametî ye... û xwedê
