rengîn, a delal, biparêzînin û bixefirînin ji qeza û belayê
vê ye jî teb'en.
 
You are welcome, you are welcome. We wish you too, and our
Kurds, all of them congratulations... This Xidir Liyas
Holiday... the Haji of Mirazan Holiday... is a holiday of
